results.name: Numbers A associated with the records of the merit function of the ABC conjecture admitting only C which are powers of 23.
comment: If records of the ABC merit function are listed scanning only parameters C of the form 23^x as described in A147642, a(n) is the value of A associated with B=A147641(n) and C=A147642(n).
